---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Catalyst Neuromorphic" description="The path to superintelligence isn't scaling the wrong architecture. It's building the right one." hasFog={true}>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="v1-hero" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v1-hero-inner">
      <p class="v1-label reveal">About</p>
      <h1 class="v1-hero-h1 reveal">AI has a hardware problem.</h1>
      <p class="v1-hero-sub reveal">We're building the processors to fix it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE PROBLEM -->
  <section class="v1-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v1-wide">
      <h2 class="v1-h2 reveal">The scaling wall</h2>
      <div class="v1-prose reveal">
        <p>Modern AI runs on hardware that was never designed for intelligence. GPUs burn hundreds of watts per chip. Data centres already consume over 2% of global electricity, and that share is climbing fast. Training a single large language model can use more energy than a hundred homes do in a year. The models are getting bigger, but the returns are shrinking.</p>
        <p>And for all that power, these systems still can't learn from new information without being retrained from scratch. They can't run without a data centre. They can't operate without sending your data to someone else's infrastructure.</p>
        <p>The path to true superintelligence isn't throwing more power at the wrong architecture. Nature spent millions of years perfecting the most efficient computational system ever created &mdash; the brain. 20 watts. Continuous learning. Real-time processing. No cloud required. The gap between current AI and real intelligence isn't a software problem. It's a hardware problem.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DATA CENTRE IMAGE — the scaling problem visualised (fair dealing: criticism/commentary) -->
  <div class="v1-img-break reveal" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v1-img-wrap">
      <img
        src="/images/about/datacenter-colossus.jpg"
        alt="Aerial view of xAI's Colossus data centre in Memphis showing rows of diesel generators, cooling units, and power infrastructure"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
        class="v1-img"
      />
      <div class="v1-img-fade v1-img-fade--top"></div>
      <div class="v1-img-fade v1-img-fade--bottom"></div>
    </div>
    <p class="v1-img-credit">xAI's Colossus data centre, Memphis. Photo: Steve Jones / Southwings for SELC</p>
  </div>

  <!-- WHAT WE'RE BUILDING — two-column with image -->
  <section class="v1-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v1-wide">
      <h2 class="v1-h2 reveal">Neuromorphic processors</h2>
      <div class="v1-neuro-grid reveal">
        <div class="v1-prose">
          <p>Neuromorphic chips compute the way neurons do. They're event-driven &mdash; they only consume energy when there's something to process. They can learn on the hardware itself, not just run pre-trained models. They operate at the edge, on-device, without cloud dependency. And they do it at a fraction of the power cost.</p>
          <p>This technology exists. Intel has Loihi. IBM built TrueNorth. But both are closed, corporate, and inaccessible. If you're not inside those companies or their select research programmes, you don't get access. The hardware that could reshape computing is locked behind walls.</p>
          <p>Catalyst is building the open alternative. Full processor designs, published research, and a cloud platform anyone can use today. We're not asking for permission to compete with billion-dollar companies. We're just doing it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="v1-neuro-img-wrap">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1647356191320-d7a1f80ca777?w=800&q=80&auto=format"
            alt="Abstract neural pathways rendered in blue and violet light"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="v1-neuro-img"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THREE VALUES -->
  <section class="v1-section-compact" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v1-wide">
      <div class="v1-values reveal-stagger">
        <div class="v1-value">
          <svg class="v1-value-icon" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
          <h3 class="v1-value-title">Event-driven</h3>
          <p class="v1-value-desc">Energy consumed only when there's something to compute. No idle power burn.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="v1-value">
          <svg class="v1-value-icon" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
          <h3 class="v1-value-title">On-device learning</h3>
          <p class="v1-value-desc">Adapts and learns on the hardware itself. No retraining from scratch.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="v1-value">
          <svg class="v1-value-icon" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"/><rect x="2" y="14" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="6.01" y2="6"/><line x1="6" y1="18" x2="6.01" y2="18"/></svg>
          <h3 class="v1-value-title">Edge-native</h3>
          <p class="v1-value-desc">Runs on-device with no cloud dependency. Your data stays yours.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SILICON IMAGE — the goal -->
  <div class="v1-img-break reveal" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v1-img-wrap">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1598406444638-d4e842c982ab?w=1600&q=80&auto=format"
        alt="Macro photograph of a silicon wafer showing individual chip dies"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
        class="v1-img"
      />
      <div class="v1-img-fade v1-img-fade--top"></div>
      <div class="v1-img-fade v1-img-fade--bottom"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- WHERE WE ARE -->
  <section class="v1-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v1-wide">
      <h2 class="v1-h2 reveal">Where we are</h2>
      <div class="v1-prose reveal">
        <p>Two processor generations designed, built in software, and validated on real FPGA hardware. Both backed by published research you can read today. A live cloud API &mdash; run a neuromorphic network from your terminal, right now, without buying anything.</p>
        <p>We're raising funding and building toward manufactured silicon. The architecture is complete, tested, and protected by patent. A physical chip you can hold, running real neuromorphic intelligence &mdash; that's what we're moving toward.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <section class="v1-section-compact" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v1-wide">
      <div class="v1-stats reveal-stagger">
        <div class="v1-stat">
          <span class="v1-stat-num" data-count="2">0</span>
          <span class="v1-stat-label">Processor generations</span>
        </div>
        <div class="v1-stat">
          <span class="v1-stat-num" data-count="2">0</span>
          <span class="v1-stat-label">Published papers</span>
        </div>
        <div class="v1-stat">
          <span class="v1-stat-num v1-stat-num--live">1</span>
          <span class="v1-stat-label">Live cloud API</span>
        </div>
        <div class="v1-stat">
          <span class="v1-stat-num">2026</span>
          <span class="v1-stat-label">UK Patent filed</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOUNDER -->
  <section class="v1-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v1-wide">
      <h2 class="v1-h2 reveal">Founder</h2>
      <div class="v1-prose reveal">
        <p><strong class="v1-strong">Henry Shulayev Barnes</strong> &mdash; engineering student at the University of Aberdeen. Started Catalyst because the neuromorphic hardware that should exist doesn't, and the hardware that does exist isn't accessible. Currently a member of Techscaler, Scotland's tech startup community.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IP -->
  <section class="v1-section-compact" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v1-wide">
      <div class="v1-ip reveal">
        <span class="v1-ip-item"><span class="v1-ip-label">UK Patents</span> Filed February 2026</span>
        <span class="v1-ip-sep">&middot;</span>
        <span class="v1-ip-item"><span class="v1-ip-label">RTL</span> BSL 1.1 &mdash; proprietary</span>
        <span class="v1-ip-sep">&middot;</span>
        <span class="v1-ip-item"><span class="v1-ip-label">SDK</span> BSL 1.1</span>
        <span class="v1-ip-sep">&middot;</span>
        <span class="v1-ip-item"><span class="v1-ip-label">Papers</span> Open access on Zenodo</span>
        <span class="v1-ip-sep">&middot;</span>
        <span class="v1-ip-item"><span class="v1-ip-label">API Client</span> MIT &mdash; open source</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GET IN TOUCH -->
  <section class="connect-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:clamp(2.4rem,5vw,3.6rem); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.035em; line-height:1.08; text-align:center; margin-bottom:18px;">Get in touch.</h2>
    <p class="connect-email"><a href="mailto:henry@catalyst-neuromorphic.com">henry@catalyst-neuromorphic.com</a></p>
    <div class="connect-grid">
      <a href="https://github.com/catalyst-neuromorphic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="connect-card">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.4 5.4 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65S8.93 17.38 9 18v4"/><path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"/></svg>
        <span class="connect-label">GitHub</span>
        <span class="connect-sub">Source &amp; contributions</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/research" class="connect-card">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
        <span class="connect-label">Research</span>
        <span class="connect-sub">Papers &amp; benchmarks</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://ko-fi.com/catalystneuromorphic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="connect-card">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
        <span class="connect-label">Support</span>
        <span class="connect-sub">Buy us a coffee on Ko-Fi</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style is:global>
    /* =============================================
       V1 — Wide & Clean (Anthropic/Vercel style)
       with full-width atmospheric imagery
       ============================================= */

    /* Hero */
    .v1-hero {
      padding: 180px 32px 60px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .v1-hero-inner {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .v1-label {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.7);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .v1-hero-h1 {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      line-height: 1.05;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .v1-hero-sub {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.3rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
      margin-top: 24px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Wide container */
    .v1-wide {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 32px;
    }

    /* Sections */
    .v1-section {
      padding: 100px 0;
    }
    .v1-section-compact {
      padding: 60px 0;
    }

    /* Section headings */
    .v1-h2 {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    /* Prose */
    .v1-prose {
      max-width: 720px;
    }
    .v1-prose p {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.15rem);
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .v1-prose p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .v1-strong {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ── Full-width image breaks ── */
    .v1-img-break {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 32px;
    }
    .v1-img-wrap {
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      aspect-ratio: 21 / 9;
    }
    .v1-img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center 30%;
      display: block;
      filter: brightness(0.55) saturate(0.9);
    }
    .v1-img-fade {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 120px;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .v1-img-fade--top {
      top: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #050507, transparent);
    }
    .v1-img-fade--bottom {
      bottom: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, #050507, transparent);
    }
    .v1-img-credit {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      text-align: right;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    /* Three values grid */
    .v1-values {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 64px;
    }
    .v1-value-icon {
      color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.6);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .v1-value-title {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .v1-value-desc {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    }

    /* Stats row */
    .v1-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 48px;
      padding: 48px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }
    .v1-stat {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .v1-stat-num {
      display: block;
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .v1-stat-num--live {
      color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.9);
    }
    .v1-stat-label {
      display: block;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    /* Neuromorphic two-column (text + image) */
    .v1-neuro-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px;
      gap: 48px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .v1-neuro-img-wrap {
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: sticky;
      top: 120px;
    }
    .v1-neuro-img {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      filter: brightness(0.75) saturate(1.2);
      transition: filter 0.6s ease;
    }
    .v1-neuro-img-wrap:hover .v1-neuro-img {
      filter: brightness(0.9) saturate(1.35);
    }

    /* IP inline */
    .v1-ip {
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      line-height: 2.2;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    }
    .v1-ip-label {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .v1-ip-sep {
      margin: 0 14px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .v1-hero { padding: 140px 24px 40px; }
      .v1-section { padding: 80px 0; }
      .v1-wide { padding: 0 24px; }
      .v1-img-break { padding: 0 16px; }
      .v1-img-wrap { aspect-ratio: 16 / 10; }
      .v1-values { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
      .v1-neuro-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .v1-neuro-img { aspect-ratio: 16 / 9; }
      .v1-neuro-img-wrap { position: static; }
      .v1-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 32px; }
      .v1-ip-sep { display: none; }
      .v1-ip-item { display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    }

    /* Connect section */
    .connect-section { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 32px 100px; }
    .connect-email { font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; text-align: center; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 56px; }
    .connect-email a { color: rgba(59,130,246,0.8); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s; }
    .connect-email a:hover { color: #60A5FA; }
    .connect-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
    .connect-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; text-align: center; padding: 36px 24px; border-radius: 20px; text-decoration: none; color: #fff; background: linear-gradient(165deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 35%, rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 100%); backdrop-filter: blur(28px) saturate(190%) brightness(1.06); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(28px) saturate(190%) brightness(1.06); border: 1px solid transparent; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.45), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.14), inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.02); position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: box-shadow 0.5s, transform 0.3s; }
    .connect-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.55), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.18), inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
    .connect-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; border-radius: 20px; padding: 1px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59,130,246,0.22) 0%, rgba(59,130,246,0.06) 25%, rgba(59,130,246,0.02) 50%, rgba(59,130,246,0.06) 75%, rgba(59,130,246,0.18) 100%); -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0); -webkit-mask-composite: xor; mask-composite: exclude; pointer-events: none; z-index: 5; opacity: 0.55; transition: opacity 0.4s; }
    .connect-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
    .connect-card svg { color: #60A5FA; margin-bottom: 16px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
    .connect-label { font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
    .connect-sub { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); position: relative; z-index: 2; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .connect-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  </style>

</BaseLayout>
